title: Worst Date Wednesday: He Thought It Was Juice
description: Brandii tells us about the time she met a guy at a wedding and after a month of chatting they made plans to hang out.  When she showed up to his house he looked VERY different than the person she met at the wedding.  Listen to the whole story for a twist ending!
